column2: SELECT up_id, dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq(up_ra,up_dec,#) as objId FROM #upload WHERE dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq(up_ra,up_dec,#) IS NOT NULL EXEC spExecuteSQL &&&'&&&+ cast(x.objId as varchar(#)) + &&&&&& as objID, dbo.fPhotoTypeN(p.type) as type, p.petroMag_u, p.petroMagErr_u, p.petroMag_g, p.petroMagErr_g, p.petroMag_r, p.petroMagErr_r, p.petroMag_i, p.petroMagErr_i, p.petroMag_z, p.petroMagErr_z, p.extinction_u, p.extinction_g, p.extinction_r, p.extinction_i, p.extinction_z, r.petroRad_r FROM #upload u JOIN #x x ON x.up_id = u.up_id JOIN SpecPhotoAll p ON p.objID = x.objID JOIN PhotoObjAll r ON r.objID = p.objID AND p.sciencePrimary=# ORDER by x.up_id &&&#', @log=#, @filter=#
